    "data_size": 210,
    "nom_orig": "Fujii",
    "texte_orig": "I[SP]made...[SP]a[SP]little[SP]error[SP]in[SP]judgement,[SP]but...[1205][001E]\nI[SP]got[SP]the[SP]battle...[1205][001E][SP]all[SP]captured[SP]on[SP]film...",
