    "id": 26,
    "offset": 349618,
    "slot_size": 234,
    "data_size": 230,
    "nom_orig": "Yukino",
    "texte_orig": "Why...[SP]Why!?[1205][001E][SP]I[SP]still[SP]hadn't...[1205][001E][SP]I[SP]never[SP]got\nto[SP]tell[SP]him...[SP]that[SP]I[SP]liked[SP]him...[SP]that[SP]I\nloved[SP]him...!",
